Our best works include:
An enterprise knowledge sharing platform deployed at some of the most relevant unicorn tech companies like Shopify, Airbnb, and Netflix;
Consulting on Django and React development for a Y Combinator fintech startup;
Design and development of a mobile-first web product from scratch for one of the most innovative healthy food subscription companies in NY. We also escalated the platform until now, when they deliver all over the US;
Redesign and implementation of a new version for a platform that allows law firms to manage all trademarks of the US. It’s used daily by the law-departments of Fortune 100 companies.
